               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi "Vita of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi" (fols.
                     2ra-43vb) 
 II) Ṭǝntä lǝdätomu la-mänäkosat "Origin of the Monks" (fols.
                     43va-44rb)
 III) Śǝrʿāta beta krǝstiyān "Structure of the Church" (fols.
                     44va-45ra), in Amharic
 IV) Calendaric treatise (ʾAbušakǝr?): Yä-qʷǝṣǝr
                     betu 6 näw mǝnnamǝn bilu ʿǝlät kekros kalǝʿit... (fols. 45va-46vb), in
                     Amharic
 V) Malkǝʾa Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi "Image of Za-Mikāʾel ʾAragāwi"
                     (fols. 47ra-52r)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
